"Look, pathetic humans."

525
00:23:38,583 --> 00:23:39,916
[FAFNIR]
Stop it.

526
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:42,041
[TOHRU] "Huh? Why do you wish
to be a magical girl?"

527
00:23:42,125 --> 00:23:43,000
[FAFNIR]
Don't mock me.

528
00:23:43,083 --> 00:23:44,041
[TOHRU]
"Acceptable.

529
00:23:44,125 --> 00:23:45,458
You shall be a
magical girl, too."

530
00:23:45,541 --> 00:23:46,916
[FAFNIR]
I'll kill you all!

